<ul class="project-title-and-text">
    <li class="project-title">
        I Didn't Starve
    </li>

    <li class="project-type">
        Screenprint
    </li>

    <li class="project-tools">
        Photoshop, Screen Print UV Machine, Silk Screen, Acrylic Paints
    </li>

    <li class="project-objective-title">
        About
    </li>

    <li class="project-body-text">
        This screenprint is based on Episode 116: 'Something Blue' from the bi-weekly podcast 'Lore'.
        A pile of blue pills — the image reframes the scammer's promise of "healing through fasting"
        as something more sinister.
    </li>
</ul>

